description:
The v-shaped cross section delivers excellent strength and holding power for a modest weight. 2 notches at the top, plus a hole at the top for security in wild conditions. Notches halfway down let you put the guy line flush against the ground even where you can't hammer the peg in fully.

  • Made from light, strong TH72M-T6 aluminum
  • Length is 16cm
  • Long, tapered point makes them easy to drive in
name: MEC J-Stake 16cm Tent Peg
